@geindex IndexDeclaredItems() (pyGHDL.dom.Concurrent.ConcurrentBlockStatement method)
@anchor{pyGHDL/pyGHDL dom Concurrent pyGHDL dom Concurrent ConcurrentBlockStatement IndexDeclaredItems}@anchor{2a4}
@deffn {Method} IndexDeclaredItems ()

Index declared items listed in the concurrent declaration region.

@*Return type: 
None@footnote{https://docs.python.org/3/library/constants.html#None}


@subsubheading Algorithm



@enumerate 

@item 
Iterate all declared items:


@itemize *

@item 
Every declared item is added to @code{_namespace}.

@item 
If the declared item is a FullType@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Type.html#pyVHDLModel.Type.FullType}, then add an entry to @ref{2a5,,_types}.

@item 
If the declared item is a @code{SubType}, then add an entry to @ref{2a6,,_subtypes}.

@item 
If the declared item is a Function@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Subprogram.html#pyVHDLModel.Subprogram.Function}, then add an entry to @ref{2a7,,_functions}.

@item 
If the declared item is a Procedure@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Subprogram.html#pyVHDLModel.Subprogram.Procedure}, then add an entry to @ref{2a8,,_procedures}.

@item 
If the declared item is a Constant@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Object.html#pyVHDLModel.Object.Constant}, then add an entry to @ref{2a9,,_constants}.

@item 
If the declared item is a Signal@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Object.html#pyVHDLModel.Object.Signal}, then add an entry to @ref{2aa,,_signals}.

@item 
If the declared item is a Variable@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Object.html#pyVHDLModel.Object.Variable}, TODO.

@item 
If the declared item is a SharedVariable@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Object.html#pyVHDLModel.Object.SharedVariable}, then add an entry to @ref{2ab,,_sharedVariables}.

@item 
If the declared item is a File@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Object.html#pyVHDLModel.Object.File}, then add an entry to @ref{2ac,,_files}.

@item 
If the declared item is neither of these types, call @code{_IndexOtherDeclaredItem()}. 
Derived classes may override this virtual function.
@end itemize
@end enumerate


@subsubheading See also



@table @asis

@item pyVHDLModel.Design.IndexPackages()@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.html#pyVHDLModel.Design.IndexPackages}

Iterate all packages in the design and index declared items.

@item pyVHDLModel.Library.IndexPackages()@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.html#pyVHDLModel.Library.IndexPackages}

Iterate all packages in the library and index declared items.

@item @code{pyVHDLModel.Library._IndexOtherDeclaredItem()}

Iterate all packages in the library and index declared items.
@end table

@end deffn

