@geindex IndexDeclaredItems() (pyGHDL.dom.DesignUnit.Entity method)
@anchor{pyGHDL/pyGHDL dom DesignUnit pyGHDL dom DesignUnit Entity IndexDeclaredItems}@anchor{3b2}
@deffn {Method} IndexDeclaredItems ()

Index declared items listed in the concurrent declaration region.

@*Return type: 
None@footnote{https://docs.python.org/3/library/constants.html#None}


@subsubheading Algorithm



@enumerate 

@item 
Iterate all declared items:


@itemize *

@item 
Every declared item is added to @code{_namespace}.

@item 
If the declared item is a FullType@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Type.html#pyVHDLModel.Type.FullType}, then add an entry to @ref{3b3,,_types}.

@item 
If the declared item is a @code{SubType}, then add an entry to @ref{3b4,,_subtypes}.

@item 
If the declared item is a Function@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Subprogram.html#pyVHDLModel.Subprogram.Function}, then add an entry to @ref{3b5,,_functions}.

@item 
If the declared item is a Procedure@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Subprogram.html#pyVHDLModel.Subprogram.Procedure}, then add an entry to @ref{3b6,,_procedures}.

@item 
If the declared item is a Constant@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Object.html#pyVHDLModel.Object.Constant}, then add an entry to @ref{3b7,,_constants}.

@item 
If the declared item is a Signal@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Object.html#pyVHDLModel.Object.Signal}, then add an entry to @ref{3b8,,_signals}.

@item 
If the declared item is a Variable@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Object.html#pyVHDLModel.Object.Variable}, TODO.

@item 
If the declared item is a SharedVariable@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Object.html#pyVHDLModel.Object.SharedVariable}, then add an entry to @ref{3b9,,_sharedVariables}.

@item 
If the declared item is a File@footnote{https://vhdl.github.io/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel/pyVHDLModel.Object.html#pyVHDLModel.Object.File}, then add an entry to @ref{3ba,,_files}.

@item 
If the declared item is neither of these types, call @code{_IndexOtherDeclaredItem()}. 
Derived classes may override this virtual function.
@end itemize
@end enumerate


