@geindex LinkArchitectures() (pyGHDL.dom.NonStandard.Library method)
@anchor{pyGHDL/pyGHDL dom NonStandard pyGHDL dom NonStandard Library LinkArchitectures}@anchor{73c}
@deffn {Method} LinkArchitectures ()

Link all architectures to corresponding entities.

@*Return type: 
None@footnote{https://docs.python.org/3/library/constants.html#None}


@subsubheading Algorithm



@enumerate 

@item 
Iterate all architecture groups (grouped per entity symbol’s name).


@itemize *

@item 
Check if entity symbol’s name exists as an entity in this library.
@end itemize


@enumerate 

@item 
For each architecture in the same architecture group:


@itemize *

@item 
Add architecture to entities architecture dictionary @code{pyVHDLModel.DesignUnit.Entity._architectures}.

@item 
Assign found entity to architecture’s entity symbol @code{pyVHDLModel.DesignUnit.Architecture._entity}

@item 
Set parent namespace of architecture’s namespace to the entitie’s namespace.

@item 
Add an edge in the dependency graph from the architecture’s corresponding dependency vertex to the entity’s corresponding dependency vertex.
@end itemize
@end enumerate
@end enumerate

@*Raises: 

@itemize *

@item 
@code{VHDLModelException} – If entity name doesn’t exist.

@item 
@code{VHDLModelException} – If architecture name already exists for entity.
@end itemize


@*Return type: 
None



