@anchor{pyGHDL/pyGHDL libghdl pyGHDL libghdl _get_libghdl_path}@anchor{14bd}
@deffn {Function} pyGHDL.libghdl._get_libghdl_path ()

Locate the directory where the shared library is installed.

`Search order:'


@enumerate 

@item 
Check environment variable @code{GHDL_PREFIX} - directory (prefix) of the vhdl libraries.

@item 
Check environment variable @code{VUNIT_GHDL_PATH} - path of the @code{ghdl} binary when using VUnit.

@item 
Check environment variable @code{GHDL} - name of, or path to the @code{ghdl} binary.

@item 
Try within @code{pyGHDL/lib} Python package installation path.

@item 
Try searching the @code{ghdl} binary via @code{which}.

@item 
Try @code{../../lib} when running from the build directory.
@end enumerate

@*Return type: 
Path@footnote{https://docs.python.org/3/library/pathlib.html#pathlib.Path}

@end deffn

